      <hedline>
        <hl1>'The Green Bird' Is Closing</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>The Green Bird, Julie Taymor's Broadway production of Carlo Gozzi's satirical fairy tale about royal orphans, announces closing (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''The Green Bird,'' Julie Taymor's production of Carlo Gozzi's satirical fairy tale about royal orphans, is to close after the matinee on Sunday at the Cort Theater, 138 West 48th Street, Manhattan. The show will have run for 55 regular performances and 16 previews.</p>
      </block>
